  render_p(sec, "Y chromosome disappearing: phi(2310) = phi(1155) = 480. Removing D preserves phi. The Y IS the biological D-channel — and D is the cheapest to lose. Species that lost Y: SRY gene migrated to autosomes. D-information migrates to other channels. D is the bridge, not the foundation.");
